Detailed Description

template<typename EvalT, typename Traits>
class LCM::ThermoMechanicalEnergyResidual< EvalT, Traits >

ThermMechanical Energy Residual.

This evaluator computes the residual for the energy equation in the coupled therm-mechanical problem
